OL,3,CAirport looking for aspiring engineers
OL,4,Cto join 'leading' apprenticeship scheme
OL,6,Fis on the hunt for future engineers.
OL,8,FNow in its 47thyear, its engineering
OL,9,Fapprenticeship programme has seen more
OL,10,Fthan 300 people graduate since 1977.
OL,12,FThe airport is recruiting four new
OL,13,Fapprentices to start in August.
OL,15,FThe four-year programme includes a
OL,16,Fyear at East Surrey College in
OL,17,FRedhill, where the apprentices will
OL,18,Fstudy practical and theory-based
OL,19,Fsubjects, working towards a BTEC level
OL,20,Fthree.
