OL,3,CAirport looking for aspiring engineers
OL,4,Cto join 'leading' apprenticeship scheme
OL,6,FThe programme gives aspiring engineers
OL,7,Fthe opportunity to earn while they are
OL,8,Flearning.
OL,10,FApprentices gain hands-on experience
OL,11,Fof various engineering sectors across
OL,12,Fthe airport, including airfield,
OL,13,Fbaggage, Specialist Systems, shuttles,
OL,14,Fand heating, ventilation and air
OL,15,Fconditioning (HVAC).
OL,17,FSuccessful completion of the
OL,18,Fapprenticeship will lead to the
OL,19,Fapprentices becoming a fully-qualified
OL,20,FEngineering Technician, with industry-
OL,21,Fstandard recognised qualifications.
