OL,3,CAirport looking for aspiring engineers
OL,4,Cto join 'leading' apprenticeship scheme
OL,6,FGatwick currently has17 engineering
OL,7,Fapprenticesacross four cohorts,
OL,8,Ftaking on an equal split of male and
OL,9,Ffemale engineering candidates for the
OL,10,Ffirst time in 2021.
OL,12,FThe airport's successful
OL,13,Fapprenticeship programmewas
OL,14,Frecognised with second place in the
OL,15,FTop 100 Apprenticeship Employers in
OL,16,Fthe Rate My Apprenticeship Awards in
OL,17,Fboth 2021-22 and 2022-23.
OL,19,FGatwick was also placed as one of the
OL,20,Fleading apprenticeship providers in
OL,21,Fthe UK last year.
